listings.description: This fully leased 7,200 SF retail center at 1808 W Lindsey St, Norman, OK is located at the SW corner of Lindsey St. and McGee St., just 1.5 miles from the University of Oklahoma. The property sits on 0.87 acres and is zoned C-2. Built in 2007, it features four units with NNN leases, 170 feet of frontage along Lindsey St., and 40 parking spaces. Situated in a high-traffic retail area with easy access to I-35, this property offers strong visibility and consistent foot traffic, making it a solid investment opportunity.

The property is being sold as-is, offering endless potential for redevelopment or income generation in a high-visibility location.

These three tracts, ranging from 9.93 to 10.57 acres, offer exceptional potential. Don't miss out on this prime location to realize your business's full potential. Act now and seize this rare gem! Listed at $499,000.00. Call today for more information.
